# Javascript-and-SVG-Animation-gr.-color-
Javascript development animation on stages with time of ejecution movement colors opening and closing a circle gradiant colors. Added as footer an SVG animation gradiant colors with background of gradiant linear developed as a set for Rober Villar from SOFTWARE RVG

